android.car.occupantawareness

类 OccupantAwarenessDetection

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.occupantawareness.OccupantAwarenessDetection

  • public final class OccupantAwarenessDetection
extends java.lang.Object
    Complete detection result for a single detected person. Includes presence detection, GazeDetection and DriverMonitoringDetection.

    Register to listen to events via OccupantAwarenessManager.
